{"tid":194743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[FB轉貼] 敍利亞人都頂唔撚順極度軟弱既美國民主黨,受訪時終於要爆啦","createTime":"2017-04-10T07:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T09:07:17.000Z","uid":31637,"like":76,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c83b2a2897a41a71d0cc632ff7358154a68a70ff","tid":194743,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s3uaf1NFxXc&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds3uaf1NFxXc%26feature%3Dshare&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b2bbaa1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s3uaf1NFxXc&amp;feature=share</a><br />\nCNN片段。<br />\n一位喺2013年化武攻擊中生還嘅敍利亞男子，<br />\n日前接受CNN訪問時，坦言感激特朗普發射戰斧巡航導彈。<br />\n主播於是「提醒」佢：<br />\n「但呢個人亦係下禁令唔准敍利亞難民入境美國嘅人喎&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n之後仲補多腳，回帶一段希拉莉發言：<br />\n「你唔能夠一邊話要保護敍利亞啲BB，一邊閂大閘。」<br />\n然後主播問：你點睇？<br />\n到咗呢個moment，呢位敍利亞受訪者終於要爆喇。<br />\n「恕我直言，反對入境禁令果班人，<br />\n喺三日前去哂邊？2013年化武攻擊時去哂邊？<br />\n當年奧巴馬無動於衷，果班人又喺邊？<br />\n如果真係關心難民，想幫我哋，唔該幫我哋留喺自己國家！<br />\n其實我哋根本唔想做難民，唔想走難嚟美國！<br />\n我哋只係想留喺自己國家！有尊嚴咁繼續喺度生活！<br />\n恕我直言，你哋呢啲叫偽善！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/limszewah/posts/10156034569627571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flimszewah%2Fposts%2F10156034569627571&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e0dbcdcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/limszewah/posts/10156034569627571</a>"},{"pid":"ae5e30d8a9e04045b9545bf6b7ce8ef40f8a9740","tid":194743,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"Trump is a hero<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a850650f2bd4d879fd8a0d52bdc4e7f6af607d4a","tid":194743,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"又一巴打落左膠度<br />\n做野永遠唔用腦"},{"pid":"3728f49d3f9f6f736e9d6a04eaedc7c04b2d8f1c"